Tekashi 6ix9ine is once again making headlines, this time for a lawsuit that saw an adult dancer end up in the hospital. Dr. Seuss has been cancelled, and on his birthday, what a shame, but really, you gotta stick around to find out who’s to blame. Little rhyme there for ya.
